title: Just Australian Planes
brief_description: Narrated by Aden Wickes, Senior Check Captain with Qantas, this film contains extraordinary rare footage of different kinds of aeroplanes, past and present, and their respective pilots. It charts a unique aeronautical journey in time, from the beginnings of the RAAF to the more fanciful, high tech aircraft of today.
